transcript.text: Hello everyone, thank you so much for your time today in spite of lockdown and all our team working from home.
As per our commitment to help our client grow, we are happy to present our latest on Print Shop V 7.3 with more features, better experience and usability.
Version 7.3 is a result of feedback from our hundreds of clients and best practices followed by printers globally.
It will help you offer better and personalized experience to your B2CB2B reseller and working clients.
This video is about B 7.3 overview of key upgrades and for all upgrades you can visit our website on printshop.com.
Below topics I am going to cover during the complete session.
So first of all I will give highlights on admin section key enhancement.
So let's check same.

Starting from simplifying code management, one of our customer shared the challenge that they are receiving multiple codes via e-mail and even the code approval is also coming offline over emails or calls.
So in earlier solution version it was difficult to convert those order code to order where the code approval was coming offline.
So for simplifying the quotation to order process, we have enhanced the code model and now printer can convert the code into order from admin itself.
It will help and empower the print company to handle those kind of code where the approval will come on emails or calls.
Although same time they will get the quote report for analyzing the success rate of shared quotation and esthetize the business accordingly.
Now the next upgrade is enhancement in shipping calculation.
In our earlier solution version we introduced the option of master package creation for all the products which is helping printers to manage package configuration in easy way for different products.
But in few cases it was leading to huge wastage of space and additional package cost also.
So customers shared that they are looking option to manage fixed size multiple product package coming in same order.
Hence for minimizing the package waste and additional cost we have developed easy package configuration for fixed size product coming in same order.
Also we have further enhanced our reporting section where now before exporting the report you can select the field headers you want to extract in report.
So it will generate the specific data as per your need.
Now the next enhancement is in e-mail notification.
Now printer will have more control on e-mail notification.
They can decide which e-mail should go to customer or internal team or both.
So after admin we have done various enhancement and upgrading storefront features as well which will improvise the customer's buying experience.
So let's check the key enhancement starting from uploaded PDF preview.

For improvising the user interaction at Design Upload Center, we have developed the file review option at upload center so that any customer can easily verify their uploaded PDF artwork in price calculator.

For enhancing buying experience we have developed option where based on the selected product attribute the specific image will reflect in image gallery which will give more idea about selected option to the customer.

Also for increasing e-mail masses effectiveness we have redesigned all the emails where you can put different subject line dynamic content and also can create template based branding on different colors as well.
Also, we have improvised the visual proofing tool UI which which help printers to reduce the artwork approval communication.
Now in this version, we have enhanced the UI as well to give the better experience to your client while approving the artwork online.
Along with the admin and storefront.
We have done many enhancement and upgraded design tool as well to improvise the customer's designing experience.
So let's see the key enhancement starting from mobile theme and advanced editing.
As per research, 66% of the global population owns a smartphone in 2020 and 79% of the smartphone user have made a purchase online using their mobile devices.
For improvising the customer's buying experience from mobile device, we have upgraded solution with the mobile theme and personalization option.
Also for enhancing the design experience we have developed option where customer can have same background in all pages in single click itself.
Now the next enhancement is quick accessibility of customer portfolio.
Now customer can access their portfolio in Design 2 directly based on the different products.
Apart from that we have done 50 plus features and enhancement for which you can refer this URL help dot on printshop.com as well.
Along with enhancement in standard SAS solution feature, we have introduced the new add-ons modules and enhanced the existing ones also.

So starting with the new photo print add on module ads, research indicates that the photo printing and the merchandise market is expected to grow by $4.68 billion during 20 to 24 and most of the photos are getting clicked from mobile devices only.

So for helping printers to expand their photo product offering we are happy to introduce new add on module Photo print which is a specifically designed for photo printers where customer can upload multiple photo and order in single click.
We also have enhanced the canvas module to next level where customer can design, preview and order split photo and multiple photo canvas with same previous simulator.
Also for enhancing the buying experience and support we have integrated WhatsApp business API and customer review application stamp as well.
With the help of WhatsApp, you can send notification, order alerts, shipping alerts and discount to your registered customer.
We are confident that version 7.3 will help you offer better services to your clients and improve the productivity.
Contact us to know more or set up online training.
Thank you for watching this video.
